  "text": [
    "Hand me this hand",
    "The sail is bent",
    "The trail is sold",
    "and the wind tied in knots",
    "Answer the phone",
    "The tune is left",
    "The stones uncoil",
    "in a wide-angle lens",
    "A search for clues",
    "encounters bliss",
    "A lip on the edge",
    "of the flowering dark",
    "A shell falls with hail",
    "Hidden and hides",
    "The following sky",
    "The descending kiss."
  ],
  "title": "Fade to Light",
  "year": ""
